{
  "stem": "8212.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a beautiful hotel in Lucerne, because the Swiss-- there was absolutely no tourist business.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there, I really tried-- by that time I was 16, and I really wanted to do fashion, or art, something to do with art.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was very eager to learn something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in Lucerne, they sent me to a place to learn how to do ceramics to start with.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I learned how to do vases-- ceramics with strips of earth, and work them and turn them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was quite nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was very cold in the winter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I got a lot of-- my hands and my feet got chilblains all over from that work with the very cold earth.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I-- I wrote to lots of people, to committees, et cetera, to be able to go to an art school.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after-- but I didn't succeed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Instead, they sent me to Bern, where a Jewish family said they would take care of me and send me to a school.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then it turned out that they really just wanted to have a-- an in-servant, somebody who does things in the kitchen, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I sta-- stayed there a few months and I was very unhappy, because they didn't send me to any school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I asked to go back to camp, which I was allowed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Whereas my sister was sent to another family, a Swiss family, not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were wonderful people and they taught her a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she went to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They sent her to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They didn't send me to school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I returned to camp, and I started writing for art schools.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At one point, I got a scholarship for Geneva.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was in 1945.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
